{"id":63,"parent_id":30,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":63,"title":"2 Nephi 33","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Ne.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 33"],[".studySummary",["i","Nephi’s words are true—They testify of Christ—Those who believe in Christ will believe Nephi’s words, which will stand as a witness before the judgment bar. About 559–545",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.1","order":"05.13.033.6943"},["b","1"],"And now I, Nephi, cannot write all the things which were taught among my people; neither am I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"mighty"],"in writing, like unto speaking; for when a man",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"speaketh"],"by the power of the Holy Ghost the power of the Holy Ghost carrieth it unto the hearts of the children of men."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.2","order":"05.13.033.6944"},["b","2"],"But behold, there are many that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"harden"],"their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"hearts"],"against the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"Holy Spirit"],", that it hath no place in them; wherefore, they cast many things away which are written and esteem them as things of naught."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.3","order":"05.13.033.6945"},["b","3"],"But I, Nephi, have written what I have written, and I esteem it as of great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"worth"],", and especially unto my people. For I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"pray"],"continually for them by day, and mine",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"eyes"],"water my pillow by night, because of them; and I cry unto my God in faith, and I know that he will hear my cry."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.4","order":"05.13.033.6946"},["b","4"],"And I know that the Lord God will consecrate my prayers for the gain of my people. And the words which I have written in weakness will be made strong unto them; for it",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"persuadeth"],"them to do good; it maketh known unto them of their fathers; and it speaketh of Jesus, and persuadeth them to believe in him, and to endure to the end, which is life",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"eternal"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.5","order":"05.13.033.6947"},["b","5"],"And it speaketh",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"harshly"],"against sin, according to the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"plainness"],"of the truth; wherefore, no man will be angry at the words which I have written save he shall be of the spirit of the devil."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.6","order":"05.13.033.6948"},["b","6"],"I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"glory"],"in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"plainness"],"; I glory in truth; I glory in my Jesus, for he hath",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"redeemed"],"my soul from hell."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.7","order":"05.13.033.6949"},["b","7"],"I have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"charity"],"for my people, and great faith in Christ that I shall meet many souls spotless at his judgment-seat."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.8","order":"05.13.033.6950"},["b","8"],"I have charity for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Jew"],"—I say Jew, because I mean them from whence I came."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.9","order":"05.13.033.6951"},["b","9"],"I also have charity for the Gentiles. But behold, for none of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"these"],"can I hope except they shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"reconciled"],"unto Christ, and enter into the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"narrow"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_9d"},"gate"],", and",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_9e"},"walk"],"in the",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_9f"},"strait"],"path which leads to life, and continue in the path until the end of the day of",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_9g"},"probation"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.10","order":"05.13.033.6952"},["b","10"],"And now, my beloved brethren, and also",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Jew"],", and all ye ends of the earth, hearken unto these words and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"believe"],"in Christ; and if ye believe not in these words believe in Christ. And if ye shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"believe"],"in Christ ye will believe in these",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"words"],", for they are the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_10e"},"words"],"of Christ, and he hath given them unto me; and they",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_10f"},"teach"],"all men that they should do good."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.11","order":"05.13.033.6953"},["b","11"],"And if they are not the words of Christ, judge ye—for Christ will show unto you, with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"power"],"and great",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"glory"],", that they are his words, at the last day; and you and I shall stand face to face before his bar; and ye shall know that I have been commanded of him to write these things, notwithstanding my weakness."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.12","order":"05.13.033.6954"},["b","12"],"And I pray the Father in the name of Christ that many of us, if not all, may be saved in his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"kingdom"],"at that great and last day."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.13","order":"05.13.033.6955"},["b","13"],"And now, my beloved brethren, all those who are of the house of Israel, and all ye ends of the earth, I speak unto you as the voice of one",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"crying"],"from the dust: Farewell until that great day shall come."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.14","order":"05.13.033.6956"},["b","14"],"And you that will not partake of the goodness of God, and respect the words of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Jews"],", and also my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"words"],", and the words which shall proceed forth out of the mouth of the Lamb of God, behold, I bid you an everlasting farewell, for these words shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"condemn"],"you at the last day."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.15","order":"05.13.033.6957"},["b","15"],"For what I seal on earth, shall be brought against you at the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"judgment"],"bar; for thus hath the Lord commanded me, and I must",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"obey"],". Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.1a","order":"05.13.033.6958"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/12.23.23-27"},"Ether 12:23 (23–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.1b","order":"05.13.033.6960"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.17.13-17"},"Rom. 10:17 (13–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.8.7-8"},"D&C 100:8 (7–8)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-gifts-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Gifts of"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.2a","order":"05.13.033.6962"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/15.31.30-31"},"Num. 15:31 (30–31)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/19.7"},"1 Ne. 19:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/4.14"},"Jacob 4:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/3.7.4-13"},"D&C 3:7 (4–13)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hardheartedness"},"TG Hardheartedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.2b","order":"05.13.033.6964"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spiritual-blindness"},"TG Spiritual Blindness"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.2c","order":"05.13.033.6966"},["b","2c"],["a.s